Package com.irurueta.navigation.geodesic.wmm

Class WMMLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.geodesic.wmm.WMMLoader
  • public class WMMLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Loads a WWM from a file of coefficients. The file of coefficients is updated every 5 years and can be obtained at: https://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/geomag/WMM/
    See Also:
